<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10150890>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Bulbophyllum longiflorum. A. Flowering plant. B & C. Inflorescence. D. Floral bract. E. Flower, half-side view and view from back. F. Dorsal sepal, abaxial and adaxial side. G. Lateral sepals, adaxial and abaxial side. H. Petals, abaxial and adaxial side. I. Magnified abaxial surface of petal. J. Lip, views from different sides. K. Ovary, petals and column, side view. L. Pedicel, ovary, and column, side view. M. Ovary, column, and lip, side view. N. Column, view from above. O. column apex, front view. P. Anther cap, view from below and from above. All photo by Truong Ba Vuong from specimen BV 1222, photo correction and design by L. Averyanov and T. Maisak." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10150890/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

